HB 203 Original 2026 Regular Session Walters
Abstract: Provides for the membership of the Uterine Fibroids Commission.
Present law provides for the Uterine Fibroids Commission within the La. Dept. of Health.
Present law provides that one member of the commission shall be nominated from Christus
Health System.
